  "text": "Most cancers have p53 gene mutations. However both sites, and types of mutations, differ among cancers of different tissue origin [CITATION_1] . In hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC) mutation within the p53 gene occurs mainly at codon 249 [CITATION_2] .",
